snippet.title: Last Fish Trailer
snippet.description:
Last Fish is available for Android and iOS.

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.pyrosphere.lastfish
App Store: http://itunes.apple.com/app/last-fish/id406432450?mt=8&ls=1

Last Fish is a stylish black and white action game about the survival of a tiny fish in toxic water filled with goo.

Eat food, avoid goo, escape the shadowfish. Survive.

http://pyrosphere.net/lastfish/
